{"tid":2144214,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】彭博引述消息：美國最早今日宣布制裁林鄭月娥及其他內地官員","createTime":"2020-08-07T14:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T14:32:11.000Z","uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2045211d3628f2fa263d6662e6706d77aba765","tid":2144214,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5019813/org/7952f25fea356f465cb38df533fdacfd.jpg/hDr1oV45GTSw4woyqwSmfZ2pk4XKub9KA_qmAAP6pgA?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5019813%2Forg%2F7952f25fea356f465cb38df533fdacfd.jpg%2FhDr1oV45GTSw4woyqwSmfZ2pk4XKub9KA_qmAAP6pgA%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=e0569b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彭博早前已曾披露，特朗普團隊早已準備好制裁名單，當中包括負責港澳事務的中共中央政治局常委韓正、特首林鄭月娥、警務處處長鄧炳強等。除此之外，由英國上下議院多名國會議員組成的「跨黨派國會香港小組」日前亦建議，針對特首林鄭月娥、警務處處長鄧炳強等侵害人權的高級官員，以《馬格尼茨基法》實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥早前被傳媒問到如何回應制裁，表示政府評估認為可以應付，更指如對方使出「核子手段」則會兩敗俱傷。"},{"pid":"929f2a660119088a488f1856e6e730cb35dd5cf3","tid":2144214,"uid":12463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:30:37.000Z","msg":"咁最遲幾時？"},{"pid":"7e198b812c8a1c02b2df8c515f591022f8ef3bc0","tid":2144214,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"929f2a660119088a488f1856e6e730cb35dd5cf3","tid":2144214,"uid":12463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:30:37.000Z","msg":"咁最遲幾時？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"24小時內 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b4b9fd90631e4c21c367f5370c93327ce26cb4","tid":2144214,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:32:11.000Z","msg":"林鄭死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}